title: Qualcomm CEO Steve Mollenkopf attended Barack Obama state dinner for China's Xi Jinping.
text:
Qualcomm CEO Steve Mollenkopf — Courtesy of Qualcomm + Read Caption Qualcomm CEO Steve Mollenkopf / Courtesy of Qualcomm 
Share Photo
   ✉ On a high (tech) note: Qualcomm CEO Steve Mollenkop f had a busy week last week. On Sept. 23, he was with top tech CEOs at a U.S.-China Internet industry forum in Seattle, where China’s President Xi Jinping briefly joined them.
Two days later, Mollenkopf and his wife, Susan, attended President Barack Obama’s State Dinner honoring the Chinese leader during his official visit here.
Other titans of high tech and social media on the guest list: Apple CEO Tim Cook , Oracle’s Larry Ellison, Netflix co-founder Reed Hastings, LinkedIn’s Reid Hoffman , Microsoft CEO Satya Nadella, IBM President Virginia Rometty and Facebook’s Mark Zuckerberg. 
The smartphones must have been buzzing…
